MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the WA3 postcode area of Warrington affecting properties in  Gosling Road, Eaves Brow and surrounding areas. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at  08:32AM. Repairs are taking longer than expected because of an underground cable fault and our team are now working to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 1.30PM. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 11:00AM on 26th January 2021
